---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Biryani with Carrots and Dried Currants and Crispy Chana Dal
description: Biryani or 'spiced rice' is an Indian mixed rice dish. Tadka Masala is a combination of dried onions, garlic, ginger and  spices that makes this dish burst with flavour!
